{% assign titleBox_center= 'mx-auto text-center mb-12 w-11/12 sm:w-2/3 xl:w-2/5' %}
{%- comment -%}居左显示主文本容器尺寸及距底部距离{%- endcomment -%}
{% assign titleBox_left= 'mx-auto text-left mb-12 w-11/12 sm:w-2/3 xl:w-2/5' %}
{%- comment -%}副标题h3尺寸及垂直外边距{%- endcomment -%}
{% assign subTitleClass = 'text-xl sm:txet-2xl font-bold my-6' %}
